OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773695157
OL,3,CFather of baby who died of
OL,4,Ccatastrophic brain injury found guilty
OL,5,Cof murder
OL,7,FThis article contains details that
OL,8,Fsome readers may find distressing
OL,10,FThe father of a five week old baby who
OL,11,Fdied of a "catastrophic" brain injury
OL,12,Fafter suffering more than 40 rib
OL,13,Ffractures during repeated assaults has
OL,14,Fbeen found guilty of her murder.
OL,16,FDarcy Leigh Jefferson also had
OL,17,Ffractures to both of her legs which
OL,18,Fwere caused at different times during
OL,19,Fthe 10 days before she died on March
OL,20,F29 2022.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
