CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773695157
OL,3,CFather of baby who died of
OL,4,Ccatastrophic brain injury found guilty
OL,5,Cof murder
OL,7,FThe jury today found Sean Jefferson,
OL,8,Fof Birch Court, Walsall guilty of
OL,9,Fmurder and two counts of causing
OL,10,Fgrevious bodily harm with intent.
OL,12,FDarcy's mother Amy Clark, 34, from
OL,13,FLichfield was found guilty of causing
OL,14,For allowing the death of a child and
OL,15,Ftwo counts of causing or allowing
OL,16,Fserious harm to a child after charges
OL,17,Fof murder or manslaughter against her
OL,18,Fwere dropped by prosecutors.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773695157
OL,3,CFather of baby who died of
OL,4,Ccatastrophic brain injury found guilty
OL,5,Cof murder
OL,7,FClark was found not guilty of two
OL,8,Fcounts of grevious bodily harm with
OL,9,Fintent.
OL,11,FPolice were called by West Midlands
OL,12,FAmbulance Service on 27 March 2022
OL,13,Fafter Darcy fatally collapsed at her
OL,14,Fhome in Burntwood.
OL,16,FJefferson and Clark were both arrested
OL,17,Fthe next day and charged in May 2025.
OL,19,FPolice say that Darcy was subject to a
OL,20,Fnumber of physical assaults during her
OL,21,Flife.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773695157
OL,3,CFather of baby who died of
OL,4,Ccatastrophic brain injury found guilty
OL,5,Cof murder
OL,7,FBy the time she died, both of her legs
OL,8,Fwere fractured and she had a number of
OL,9,Frib injuries.
OL,11,FJefferson, who wore a grey tracksuit
OL,12,Fand blue adidas jacket shook his head
OL,13,Fin the dock as the jury of eight women
OL,14,Fand four men returned their unanimous
OL,15,Fverdicts on Monday.
OL,17,FThe pair will be sentenced at a future
OL,18,Fdate.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773695157
OL,3,CFather of baby who died of
OL,4,Ccatastrophic brain injury found guilty
OL,5,Cof murder
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Ian
OL,8,FFitzgerald, from the Major
OL,9,FInvestigations Department at
OL,10,FStaffordshire Police said: "Today's
OL,11,Fverdict concludes a profoundly
OL,12,Fdistressing case involving the murder
OL,13,Fof five-week-old Darcy. Her short life
OL,14,Fand tragic death must not be forgotten.
OL,16,F"Darcy was violently abused and
OL,17,Fmurdered by her father. Her mother
OL,18,Fallowed her death. These were the
OL,19,Fpeople who should have loved and cared
OL,20,Ffor her. It was despicable behaviour
OL,21,Fagainst a defenceless child.
OL,26,@rD@\OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773695157
OL,3,CFather of baby who died of
OL,4,Ccatastrophic brain injury found guilty
OL,5,Cof murder
OL,7,F"It has been an exceptionally
OL,8,Fdifficult investigation, and the
OL,9,Fthoughts of the entire investigation
OL,10,Fteam remain with her elder sibling,
OL,11,Fwho has faced an unimaginable loss and
OL,12,Fa lengthy judicial process.
OL,14,F"I wish to acknowledge the
OL,15,Fprofessionalism and dedication of the
OL,16,Fofficers and staff who have worked so
OL,17,Ftirelessly on this case, but also the
OL,18,FCPS prosecutor and barristers,
OL,19,FHarpreet Sandhu Kings Counsel and
OL,20,FJoshua Purser."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773695157
OL,3,CFather of baby who died of
OL,4,Ccatastrophic brain injury found guilty
OL,5,Cof murder
OL,7,FProsecution counsel Harpreet Sandhu KC
OL,8,Fsaid the head injury had been caused
OL,9,Fby Darcy being shaken violently or
OL,10,Fhaving her head struck against a
OL,11,Fsurface.
OL,13,FThe court heard the fatal attack must
OL,14,Fhave taken place between 7am and
OL,15,F7.18am on March 27 after Jefferson
OL,16,Ftook Darcy downstairs at their then-
OL,17,Fhome in Hudson Drive in Burntwood,
OL,18,FStaffordshire.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773695157
OL,3,CFather of baby who died of
OL,4,Ccatastrophic brain injury found guilty
OL,5,Cof murder
OL,7,F"If Darcy had been crying before she
OL,8,Fstopped breathing, as Sean Jefferson
OL,9,Fsuggested, the reality, you may think,
OL,10,Fis that Sean Jefferson put a stop to
OL,11,FDarcy crying," Mr Sandhu told the jury
OL,12,Fin his closing speech.
OL,14,F"He put a stop to Darcy screaming. He
OL,15,Fdid that by shaking his five-week-old
OL,16,Fdaughter violently.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@NO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773695157
OL,3,CFather of baby who died of
OL,4,Ccatastrophic brain injury found guilty
OL,5,Cof murder
OL,7,F"As a result, his five-week-old
OL,8,Fdaughter sustained a catastrophic head
OL,9,Finjury and she would have stopped
OL,10,Fbreathing almost as soon as she
OL,11,Freceived that fatal head injury."
OL,13,FJefferson and Clark opted not to give
OL,14,Fevidence in their defence during the
OL,15,Ftrial.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773695157
OL,3,CFather of baby who died of
OL,4,Ccatastrophic brain injury found guilty
OL,5,Cof murder
OL,7,FMr Sandhu said during his closing
OL,8,Fspeech it was their right not to give
OL,9,Fevidence but their choice not to, when
OL,10,Fthey were the only people who could
OL,11,Ftell the court what happened to Darcy,
OL,12,Fwas "telling".
OL,14,FHe said: "They have chosen to remain
OL,15,Fsilent. They have chosen to remain
OL,16,Fsilent in response to evidence about
OL,17,Fhow their daughter was injured
OL,18,Frepeatedly.
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@MO]vD@JOU
